---

#### 3.5 Property Types Ontologies

##### 3.5.1 Data Property Test (`data-property-test.owl`)

**Test scenarios:**
- Single data property (string)
- Array data property (cardinality > 1)
- Required data property (minCardinality 1)
- Data property with enum (DataOneOf)
- Data property with default (DataHasValue)
